(d) (15%) Testify the underlying assumptions of regression (1) Normality, (2) Independence, and (3) Homogeneity of Variance with respect to residual.¶

(1) Normality¶

H0: The residual is normal distribution. H1: The residual is not normal distribution.

Shapiro-Wilk test 是最常使用的常態性檢測工具，可以告訴我們隨機抽取出來的樣本是否來自於常態分布，當統計值 W 愈小，表示資料愈不可能來自常態分布。

資料來源： https://epicdatastudio.xyz/normality-test/ https://www.statology.org/shapiro-wilk-test-python/

In [73]:
# pd.set_option('display.float_format', lambda x: '%.5f' % x)
# np.set_printoptions(suppress=None)
from scipy.stats import shapiro

#perform Shapiro-Wilk test
shap_result = shapiro(res.resid)
print("ShapiroResult statistic:")
print("{:.10f}".format(shap_result[0]))
print("ShapiroResult pvalue:")
print("{:.20f}".format(shap_result[1]))

ShapiroResult statistic:
0.9345124364
ShapiroResult pvalue:
0.00000000000000075360

Kolmogorov-Smirnov test 可檢定樣本是否吻合某個特定的分布 (ex:常態分布)，統計值 D 愈大，表示資料愈不可能來自常態分布。

資料來源：https://peilee-98185.medium.com/%E6%9F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%8E%AB%E5%93%A5%E6%B4%9B%E5%A4%AB-%E6%96%AF%E7%B1%B3%E7%88%BE%E8%AB%BE%E5%A4%AB%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97-kolmogorov-smirnov-test-8d723edd5e1b

In [80]:
from scipy.stats import kstest
k_result = kstest(res.resid, 'norm')
print("KstestResult statistic:")
print("{:.10f}".format(k_result[0]))
print("KstestResult pvalue:")
print("{:.60f}".format(k_result[1]))

KstestResult statistic:
0.2661699066
KstestResult pvalue:
0.000000000000000000000000000000000000002879954970164647316860

如果樣本數少於等於50，則看 Shapiro-Wilk的 W 值，來檢測是否為常態分佈； 如果樣本數大於50，則看 Kolomogorov 的 D 值。

由上述兩個測試結果可見，p-value皆<0.05，代表拒絕虛無假設H0並有充足的證據說明residual data並非常態分佈資料。

資料來源：http://sub.chimei.org.tw/57300/images/05_research/1081125.pdf

(2) Independence¶

獨立性(Independency) : 誤差項之間應該要相互獨立，否則在估計迴歸參數時會降低統計的檢定力。

我們可以藉由Durbin-Watson test來檢查。

H0: The errors is independent. H1: The errors is not independent.

資料來源：https://www.yongxi-stat.com/simple-regression-analysis/ https://www.cupoy.com/qa/collection/0000017705894B9C000000036375706F795F72656C656173654355/00000177151DDEC3000000236375706F795F70726572656C656173654349/0000017F4D85E68A000000106375706F795F72656C656173655155455354 https://www.statology.org/durbin-watson-test-python/

In [133]:
from statsmodels.stats.stattools import durbin_watson

print("{:.10f}".format(tstatistic))

durbin_watson statistic:
2.0040534805

由上述測試結果可見，dw值在1.5~2.55之間，代表接受虛無假設H0，說明residual data相互獨立。

(3) Homogeneity¶

殘差變異數一致性：使用 Breusch-Pagan Test 檢測殘差變異數是否一致。

\begin{cases}H_{0}: \sigma^{1} = \sigma^{2} = ... = \sigma^{n} \end{cases}\begin{cases}H_{1}: \sigma^{i} \not= \sigma^{j} \end{cases}

資料來源：https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/how-to-perform-a-breusch-pagan-test-in-python/

(1) (10%) How to handle the raw dataset via data preprocessing?¶

In [135]:
import csv

set_all = set()
item_count = 0
with open("./MDS_Assignment1_groceries.csv", "r") as f:
    reader = csv.reader(f, delimiter=";")
    for i, line in enumerate(reader):
        items_list = line[0].split(',')
        for item in items_list:
            item_count += 1
            set_all.add(item)
# print(set_all)
# print(len(set_all))
# print(item_count)

# initial df with a row of zeros
df_2 = pd.DataFrame(np.zeros((1,len(set_all)), dtype=int), columns=list(set_all))
with open("./MDS_Assignment1_groceries.csv", "r") as f:
    reader = csv.reader(f, delimiter=";")
    for i, line in enumerate(reader):
        items_list = line[0].split(',')
        tmp_dic = {}
        for item in items_list:
            tmp_dic[item] = 1
        df_2 = df_2.append(tmp_dic, ignore_index=True)

# remove the first initial row of zeros
df_2 = df_2.iloc[1: , :]
df_2 = df_2.fillna(0)
df_2 = df_2.reset_index(drop=True)

  • (liquor)=>(bottled beer, red/blush wine)：罐裝啤酒與紅酒都屬於酒的類型，買了酒就可能是買罐裝啤酒或是紅酒，買了罐裝啤酒或是紅酒就是買了酒，所以前兩條規則lift很高是因為 liquor 意思相當於 bottled beer, red/blush wine。

(b) (10%)試給出最佳績效 (best case)下，最大的產出率 (THbest)與最小生產週期時間 (CTbest)的計算公式 (提示 ：講義 22-29頁)¶

Best Case:

W0 = 關鍵在製品水準 //3

r_b = 瓶頸站產出率 //0.375

T0 = W0/r_b //8

CTbest:

if w<=W0 => CT(w) = T0

if w>W0 => CT(w) = w/r_b

THbest:

if w<=W0 => TH(w) = w/T0

if w>W0 => TH(w) = r_b

In [195]:
# Best Case
W0 = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH'])*sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #15.375
r_b = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH']) #0.375
T0 = sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #41

# CTbest
# if w<=W0 => CT(w) = T0
# else => CT(w) = w/r_b
CT = []
for w in range(1,50):
    if w <= W0: CT.append(T0)
    else: CT.append(w/r_b)
print("CTbest: ", min(CT))

# THbest
# if w<=W0 => TH(w) = w/T0
# else => TH(w) = r_b
TH = []
for w in range(1,50):
    if w <= W0: TH.append(w/T0)
    else: TH.append(r_b)
print("THbest: ", max(TH))

CTbest:  41
THbest:  0.375

import matplotlib

WIP CT¶

In [197]:
# define variables
W0 = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH'])*sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #15.375
r_b = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH']) #0.375
T0 = sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #41
maxw = 25

# setup arrays for each line in the plot
wip =[] # WIP levels
CTpwc =[] # practical worst case throughput
CTw =[] # worst case throughput
CTb = [] # best case throughput
                              
# loop through formulas and fill the arrays
for i in range(1,maxw):
    wip.append(i)
    pwc = T0 + (i-1)/r_b
    CTpwc.append(pwc)
    worst = i*T0
    CTw.append(worst)
    if i <= W0:
        best = T0
    else:
        best = i/r_b
    CTb.append(best)
                    
# plot result
plt.figure(figsize = (10,5))
# plt.plot(wip, CTpwc, marker='', color='blue', linewidth=2, label="CT PWC")
# plt.plot(wip, CTw, marker='', color='red', linewidth=2, label="CT Worst")
plt.plot(wip, CTb, marker='', color='green', linewidth=2, linestyle='dashed', label="CT Best")
plt.xlabel("WIP")
plt.ylabel("CT")
plt.legend()
plt.show()

# define variables
W0 = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH'])*sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #15.375
r_b = min(df_3['加工站的產能 TH']) #0.375
T0 = sum(df_3['加工時間 t']) #41
maxw = 20

# setup arrays for each line in the plot
wip =[] # WIP levels
THpwc =[] # practical worst case throughput
THw =[] # worst case throughput
THb = [] # best case throughput
                              
# loop through formulas and fill the arrays
for i in range(1,maxw):
    wip.append([i])
    pwc = i/(W0+i-1)*r_b
    THpwc.append([pwc])
    worst = 1/T0
    THw.append([worst])
    if i<=W0:
        best = i/T0
    else:
        best = r_b
    THb.append([best])
                    
# plot result
plt.figure(figsize = (10,5))
# plt.plot(wip, THpwc, marker='', color='blue', linewidth=2, label="TH PWC")
# plt.plot(wip, THw, marker='', color='red', linewidth=2, label="TH Worst")
plt.plot(wip, THb, marker='', color='green', linewidth=2, linestyle='dashed', label="TH Best")
plt.xlabel("WIP")
plt.ylabel("TH")
plt.legend()
plt.show()
